00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:48.000
We have to boil it further down using the Whisper API from OpenAI into text.

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:56.000
So with a handful of JPEGs and some text, now we have input that GPT-4 can understand.

00:11:56.000 --> 00:12:00.000
