00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:39.000
On-prem means on-premises, meaning you're running it on your own server that you manage,

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:45.000
whether that is in your bedroom or in your data center

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:48.000
or in a cloud of your choice.

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:51.000
But if you're managing the server, then that's called on-prem,

00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:56.000
whereas the cloud offerings, you don't even know that a server exists.

