01:09:01.000 --> 01:09:06.000
I actually think, if you don't mind, Joe or Winston, I think this is actually a great place

01:09:06.000 --> 01:09:09.000
to talk about what Posit believes in.

01:09:10.000 --> 01:09:17.000
Because Posit has a very special strong stance surrounding open source in these topics.

01:09:17.000 --> 01:09:20.000
