01:09:22.000 --> 01:09:30.000
I think we do have a very strong stance around open source and less directly relevant to LLMs.

01:09:30.000 --> 01:09:37.000
But our general philosophy as a company is we believe in developing tools that help people

01:09:37.000 --> 01:09:44.000
understand the world using data and making that available to everybody regardless of economic means,

01:09:44.000 --> 01:09:47.000
which is why all of our core technology is open source.

01:09:48.000 --> 01:09:53.000
That being said, when it comes to these sort of large AI models that we don't really fully understand

01:09:53.000 --> 01:10:00.000
and don't have an accurate mental model of how they work and how we can sort of keep them safe,

01:10:00.000 --> 01:10:03.000
I think within the company there's a lot of different opinions.

01:10:03.000 --> 01:10:08.000
And I think some people are very, very optimistic and some people are very, very pessimistic.

01:10:09.000 --> 01:10:16.000
And I think there are people in the company that are working on taking this technology

01:10:16.000 --> 01:10:21.000
and making it really good for our users by enhancing the experience in our studio

01:10:21.000 --> 01:10:28.000
and letting people build tools in Shiny that help enhance their experience of working with these AIs.

01:10:28.000 --> 01:10:35.000
But we also have people at and affiliated with the company that are working on AI safety

01:10:35.000 --> 01:10:41.000
and are extremely, extremely concerned about what this means for humanity.

01:10:41.000 --> 01:10:47.000
And we have a lot of deep involvement in different efforts to make that safe.

01:10:47.000 --> 01:10:50.000
